item.title: HYDRANS - Creature [Dubstep, Experimental] :soundcloud:
item.dc:creator: Dadmother
item.description:
OKAY IT’S 7AM AND I AM TWERKING OVER MY BREAKFAST.

This is TIGHT. You definitely a have strong command over the flow of this track. Every note or texture sounds wonderfully calculated and well thought out. I’ve been working on a dubstep/trapstep tune myself, and this is definitely some good inspiration. I’m excited to hear more from you!
